ight=\"600\" fill=\"#d4548a\" letter-spacing=\"2.5\">\n          <textPath href=\"#cr\" startOffset=\"0%\">events • conway + central arkansas as cool people &amp; <\/textPath>\n        <\/text>\n      <\/svg>\n      <div class=\"ring-center\">\n        <h1>LOVE<br>LOCAL<br>GUIDE<\/h1>\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n    <p class=\"hero-sub\">Conway + Central Arkansas Cool People &amp; Events<\/p>\n  <\/div>\n  <div class=\"scroll-cue\">scroll to explore ↓<\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n<!-- ==================== LOVE LETTER ==================== -->\n<section class=\"cork-bg\">\n  <div class=\"notebook\">\n    <h2>A LOVE LETTER TO YOU<\/h2>\n    <p>Welcome to the CCPE \"Love Local\" Guide to the Conway and Central AR area.<\/p>\n    <p>This guide has been curated by the admins as a way for like-minded individuals in our area to mingle and support businesses we love. Conway (and the surrounding area) is a thriving community, teeming with diversity, local artists, and rich culture. You just have to know where to look!<\/p>\n    <p>This intro is a love letter to you: thank you for taking interest in our group and recommendations. Our community is only as big as you are.<\/p>\n    <p><em>— with love, Melody and Sydney, (CCPE Admins)<\/em><\/p>\n  <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n<!-- ==================== GUIDE KEY ==================== -->\n<section class=\"key-section\">\n  <div class=\"key-card\">\n    <h2>GUIDE KEY<\/h2>\n    <ul class=\"key-list\">\n      <li>💙 one of our personal favorite places<\/li>\n      <li>⭐ top-rated: over 4.8 stars on Google<\/li>\n      <li>✳️ has been in Conway for over 20 years<\/li>\n      <li>🌸 woman-owned business<\/li>\n      <li>🐾 pet\/dog friendly space<\/li>\n      <li>🍀 allergy or dietary accommodating<\/li>\n      <li>🎵 offers live music<\/li>\n    <\/ul>\n  <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n<!-- ==================== NAV TABS ==================== -->\n<div class=\"tabs-bar\">\n  <div class=\"tabs-inner\">\n    <button class=\"tab-btn on\"  onclick=\"show('food',this)\">🍜 Food &amp; Drink<\/button>\n    <button class=\"tab-btn\"     onclick=\"show('crawl',this)\">☕ Coffee Crawl<\/button>\n    <button class=\"tab-btn\"     onclick=\"show('retail',this)\">🛍 Shops<\/button>\n    <button class=\"tab-btn\"     onclick=\"show('selfcare',this)\">💅 Self-Care<\/button>\n    <button class=\"tab-btn\"     onclick=\"show('todo',this)\">🎭 Things To Do<\/button>\n    <button class=\"tab-btn\"     onclick=\"show('events',this)\">📅 Events<\/button>\n    <button class=\"tab-btn\"     onclick=\"show('nearby',this)\">🗺 Nearby Towns<\/button>\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<!-- ==================== FOOD ==================== -->\n<div id=\"food\" class=\"page on\">\n<div class=\"content-wrap\">\n\n  <div class=\"sec-head\"><span class=\"sec-emoji\">🍜<\/span><h2>Food, Beverage &amp; Grocery<\/h2><\/div>\n\n  <div class=\"sub-title\">🍔 Casual Eats<\/div>\n  <div class=\"grid\">\n\n    <div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-strip s-coral\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-name\">The Rogue Roundabout<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-badges\">💙<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-desc\">Local fave bar + eatery downtown. Known for good vibes and a diverse crowd. Offers outdoor, vintage clothing pop-ups every few months and IPA tastings. Great spot to land on weekends.<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-strip s-pink\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-name\">Big Bad Breakfast<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-badges\">⭐ 🍀<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-desc\">Southern breakfast done right. Expect a wait on weekends, but so worth it. Excellent for brunch dates. Allergy friendly, closes early! (It is breakfast, after all!)<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-strip s-yellow\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-name\">Bulgogi<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-badges\">⭐ 💙 🍀<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-desc\">Korean BBQ in Conway, and genuinely good. Rare find in central AR. Bring friends to share the grill. Sweet owners, nut-allergy accommodations and vegetarian options.<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-strip s-teal\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-name\">Sakura Ocean<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-badges\">🍀 ⭐<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-desc\">Japanese and sushi. A solid go-to when you're craving sushi, and they offer an excellent ALL YOU CAN EAT OPTION! Accommodates gluten-free, soy-free, and for peanut allergies.<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-strip s-purple\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-name\">Brick &amp; Forge Tap Room<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-badges\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-desc\">Craft beer bar with rotating taps and a chill atmosphere. Beer on tap here is our fav. Great for low-key hangouts and game nights, also plays other televised events like the Super Bowl, The Grammys, and more! Lots of cheap eats here, you must try the pulled pork nachos!<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-strip s-coral\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-name\">Portofino Italian<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-badges\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-desc\">Cozy Italian with a slightly more elegant atmosphere. Perfect for date night without going to Little Rock.<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-strip s-mint\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-name\">Taziki's Cafe<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-badges\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-desc\">Mediterranean with solid vegetarian and lighter options. Great for lunch.<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-strip s-pink\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-name\">David's Burgers<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-badges\">✳️<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-desc\">Arkansas legend. Smash burgers, crinkle fries, milkshakes. Free ice cream samples when you dine in.<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-strip s-yellow\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-name\">O'Malley's<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-badges\">🎵<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-desc\">Our own little Irish pub. Good bar food, drinks, and local music nights. Friendly neighborhood feel.<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-strip s-teal\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-name\">Rock N Roll Sushi<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-badges\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-desc\">Funky sushi rolls with fun names and a party playlist.<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-strip s-coral\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-name\">Stoby's<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-badges\">✳️ 🐾<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-desc\">A Conway Classic. The cheese dip is mandatory. Casual diner vibe that locals swear by.<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-strip s-purple\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-name\">La Pista<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-badges\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-desc\">Wood-fired pizza and Italian food with a vibey atmosphere, good desserts, worth the hype.<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-strip s-pink\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-name\">Roost &amp; Tap<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-badges\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-desc\">A New Favorite to the area! Southern comfort food with a tap list. Popular with the after-work crowd and live music fans.<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-strip s-yellow\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-name\">Taj Mahal<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-badges\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-desc\">Indian food in Conway, a genuine gem. Rich curries, friendly staff.<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-strip s-teal\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-name\">The Patio Cafe<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-badges\">🐾<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-desc\">Outdoor seating, casual brunch\/lunch menu. Dog-friendly patio is a big plus for people with pets!<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-strip s-coral\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-name\">Hideaway Pizza Co.<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-badges\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-desc\">Artisan pizza, a local chain with a \"summer camp\" atmosphere. Good for big groups.<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-strip s-purple\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-name\">Serrano's<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-badges\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-desc\">Tex-Mex staple. Margaritas hit different here, ask anyone. Good for a casual night out.<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-strip s-pink\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-name\">Purple Cow<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-badges\">✳️<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-desc\">Local diner chain with nostalgia energy. Great milkshakes. A uniquely AR experience.<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-strip s-teal\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-name\">U.S. Pizza Company<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-badges\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-desc\">A Conway classic. Reliable, casual, good for groups.<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-strip s-coral\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-name\">Whole Hog BBQ<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-badges\">✳️<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-desc\">Arkansas BBQ done right. Pulled pork, ribs, and a killer white potato salad. Won Best BBQ of Conway in 2023 for a reason!<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-strip s-yellow\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-name\">Lost Pizza<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-badges\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-desc\">Casual pizza spot, reliable and semi-local chain.<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-strip s-purple\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-name\">Los 3 Portillos<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-badges\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-desc\">Mexican restaurant with solid home-style cooking.<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n  <\/div><!-- \/grid casual -->\n\n  <div class=\"sub-title\">✨ Elevated Eats<\/div>\n  <div class=\"grid\">\n\n    <div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-strip s-purple\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-name\">Umami<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-badges\">💙 ⭐ 🍀<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-desc\">One of Conway's most exciting restaurants. Sushi and Pan-Asian fusion with real creative energy, especially at night. Perfect for a special night out.<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-strip s-coral\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-name\">Seven Oaks<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-badges\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-desc\">Pricey, but perfect if you are celebrating something special! (Or just balling tbh.) Upscale dining in an elevated setting. Great for celebrations or impressing that special someone.<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-strip s-pink\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-name\">Mike's Place<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-badges\">✳️<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-desc\">Classic upscale American. A Conway institution with a long history and loyal locals.<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-strip s-teal\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-name\">Pasta Grill<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-badges\">💙<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-desc\">Italian food in that mid-range that locals love. Solid pasta, good service, not a chain. Lots of great appetizers and a crazy good espresso martini.<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n  <\/div>\n\n  <div class=\"sub-title\">🚚 Food Trucks<\/div>\n  <div class=\"tip\">\n    <h4>💡 How to find them<\/h4>\n    Follow local Facebook groups like \"Conway Food Truck Scene,\" the \"Roundabout Vintage Market\" + \"Conway Art Walk\" + \"Fountaine Bleau\" + and \"Bella Rustina Vintage\" Market for more schedules — trucks rotate through events and sometimes park near UCA campus on weekday evenings. Some also have fixed locations, so call for info!\n  <\/div>\n  <div class=\"pills\">\n    <span class=\"pill p-coral\">Juan's Mexican Taqueria<\/span>\n    <span class=\"pill p-teal\">The Grind Coffee Bistro<\/span>\n    <span class=\"pill p-purple\">Arkansas Breakfast Club (Greenbrier and Conway)<\/span>\n    <span class=\"pill p-pink\">Risky Biscuits<\/span>\n    <span class=\"pill p-coral\">Uncle Tim's<\/span>\n    <span class=\"pill p-teal\">Spud Love<\/span>\n    <span class=\"pill p-yellow\">Island Snow<\/span>\n  <\/div>\n\n  <div class=\"sub-title\">🍬 Snacks &amp; Sweets<\/div>\n  <div class=\"grid\">\n\n    <div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-strip s-pink\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-name\">Kassi's Cookies<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-badges\">🌸 ⭐<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-desc\">Local, handmade, insanely good. Worth every calorie.<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-strip s-coral\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-name\">BMB Creations Bakery<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-badges\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-desc\">Custom cakes and baked goods.<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-strip s-yellow\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-name\">Gush by Presleigh<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-badges\">🌸<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-desc\">Instagramable, home-made sour candies!<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-strip s-mint\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-name\">Andy's Frozen Custard<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-badges\">🐾<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-desc\">An Arkansas Classic chain. Dog-friendly patio, incredible custard.<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-strip s-purple\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-name\">Crumbl Cookie<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-badges\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-desc\">A chain, but delicious. Weekly rotating flavors, great for sharing (or not).<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-strip s-teal\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-name\">Insomnia Cookies<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-badges\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-desc\">Late-night delivery cookies. The 2am decision you won't regret.<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n  <\/div>\n\n  <div class=\"sub-title\">☕ Coffee &amp; Beverages<\/div>\n  <div class=\"grid\">\n\n    <div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-strip s-teal\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-name\">Blue Sail Coffee<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-badges\">💙 ⭐<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-desc\">One of the most beloved spots in Conway. Beautiful drinks, great atmosphere, genuinely good espresso.<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-strip s-pink\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-name\">Demure Coffee<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-badges\">🌸 ⭐<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-desc\">Hosts the Demure Vintage Market at The Village At Hendrix, be sure to follow! A community hub.<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-strip s-coral\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-name\">Espresso at Evergreen<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-badges\">⭐<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-desc\">On Oak St., the Conway Art Walk home base. Beautiful space.<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-strip s-purple\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-name\">Secret Nook<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-badges\">💙<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-desc\">Coffee AND books. Cozy, indie, exactly what you'd design if given free reign. Also hosts events like a monthly Writer's Group!<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-strip s-yellow\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-name\">Gibson's Cat Cafe<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-badges\">💙<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-desc\">Coffee + adoptable cats. Arguably the most delightful place in Conway.<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-strip s-mint\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-name\">Rising Star Boba<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-badges\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-desc\">Boba tea spot with fun flavors.<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-strip s-coral\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-name\">Swig<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-badges\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-desc\">Fun dirty soda and energy drink customization chain based in Utah.<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n  <\/div>\n\n  <div class=\"sub-title\">🥬 Grocery &amp; Local Produce<\/div>\n  <div class=\"grid\">\n\n    <div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-strip s-teal\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-name\">El Pueblo<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-badges\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-desc\">Hispanic grocery with fresh produce, fresh meats, and imported goods you won't find at the local Walmart.<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-strip s-mint\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-name\">Bell Urban Farm Stand<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-badges\">💙<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-desc\">Hyper-local vegetables and produce, honey, and seasonal goods! Open all year round, but a can't-miss in spring. Fresh Kombucha on tap, Mountain Valley Water, and Loblolly Icecream, a local fav!<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-strip s-yellow\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-name\">Green Thumb Produce<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-badges\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-desc\">Fresh local produce market.<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-strip s-coral\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-name\">Jackson Meat Market<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-badges\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-desc\">Local butcher.<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-strip s-purple\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-name\">Squizito<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-badges\">💙<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-desc\">Local specialty grocer that offers kitchen goods. Specializes in olive oil and vinegar pairings. Get creative!<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n  <\/div>\n\n<\/div><!-- \/content-wrap food -->\n<\/div><!-- \/page food -->\n\n<!-- ==================== COFFEE CRAWL ==================== -->\n<div id=\"crawl\" class=\"page\">\n<div class=\"content-wrap\">\n\n  <div class=\"sec-head\"><span class=\"sec-emoji\">☕<\/span><h2>Coffee Crawl<\/h2><\/div>\n\n  <div class=\"tip\">\n    <h4>☕ Unofficial CCPE Coffee Crawl 2026<\/h4>\n    Hit them all and earn your caffeine badge! Start at Cross Creek or Gibson's, work your way downtown, hit Secret Nook and Espresso at Evergreen on Oak St. (perfect for Art Walk nights), and finish at Demure or Blue Sail. These coffee shops are our favorites, but also be sure to check out the OFFICIAL Conway Coffee Crawl List, available from the \"Faulkner County Caffeine Addicts\" Group on Facebook for extensive locations!\n  <\/div>\n\n  <div class=\"crawl-item\">\n    <div class=\"crawl-num\">1<\/div>\n    <div>\n      <div class=\"crawl-name\">Cross Creek Sandwich Shop<\/div>\n      <div class=\"crawl-desc\">Coffee + sandwiches. Great for a working morning.<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n\n  <div class=\"crawl-item\">\n    <div class=\"crawl-num\">2<\/div>\n    <div>\n      <div class=\"crawl-name\">Blue Sail Coffee ⭐<\/div>\n      <div class=\"crawl-desc\">One of the most beloved spots in Conway.<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n\n  <div class=\"crawl-item\">\n    <div class=\"crawl-num\">3<\/div>\n    <div>\n      <div class=\"crawl-name\">Demure Coffee 💙 🌸 ⭐<\/div>\n      <div class=\"crawl-desc\">Community hub and Demure Market host.<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n\n  <div class=\"crawl-item\">\n    <div class=\"crawl-num\">4<\/div>\n    <div>\n      <div class=\"crawl-name\">Espresso at Evergreen ⭐ 🐾<\/div>\n      <div class=\"crawl-desc\">The Art Walk home base on Oak St.<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n\n  <div class=\"crawl-item\">\n    <div class=\"crawl-num\">5<\/div>\n    <div>\n      <div class=\"crawl-name\">Secret Nook 💙<\/div>\n      <div class=\"crawl-desc\">Coffee and books. The bookshop the alt crowd claims.<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n\n  <div class=\"crawl-item\">\n    <div class=\"crawl-num\">6<\/div>\n    <div>\n      <div class=\"crawl-name\">Gibson's Cat Cafe 💙<\/div>\n      <div class=\"crawl-desc\">Coffee + adoptable cats. Reserve ahead.<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n\n  <div class=\"crawl-item\">\n    <div class=\"crawl-num\">7<\/div>\n    <div>\n      <div class=\"crawl-name\">Roll &amp; Play<\/div>\n      <div class=\"crawl-desc\">Board game cafe with coffee and drinks. D&amp;D and drinks, anyone?<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n\n  <div class=\"crawl-item\">\n    <div class=\"crawl-num\">8<\/div>\n    <div>\n      <div class=\"crawl-name\">T.H.I.N.K. Coffee ⭐<\/div>\n      <div class=\"crawl-desc\">Great espresso.<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<!-- ==================== RETAIL ==================== -->\n<div id=\"retail\" class=\"page\">\n<div class=\"content-wrap\">\n\n  <div class=\"sec-head\"><span class=\"sec-emoji\">🛍<\/span><h2>Retail &amp; Shopping<\/h2><\/div>\n\n  <div class=\"sub-title\">📚 Bookshops<\/div>\n  <div class=\"grid\">\n\n    <div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-strip s-purple\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-name\">Secret Nook<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-badges\">💙<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-desc\">Indie bookshop + coffee. Curated selection, hosts events, supports local authors.<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-strip s-pink\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-name\">Pages &amp; Ink<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-badges\">🌸<\/div>\n      <div class=\"card-desc\">Sweet, romance-only bookshop with a personal curation touch. Did I mention the CANDLE BAR? Great for gifts and discoveries. GRAND OPENING APRIL 25, 2026!<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-strip 